    <item>
      <title>中国公布欧盟调查结果 暗示将采取报复措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-says-eu-s-foreign-subsidies-law-amounts-to-trade-barrier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，欧盟为保护中国企业免受外国补贴而采取的措施是对贸易和投资的阻碍，这是双方持续贸易争端的最新冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/china-says-eu-s-foreign-subsidies-law-amounts-to-trade-barrier</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 03:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国通过创纪录的香港票据发行加大对人民币的支持</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国加大了对陷入困境的人民币的支持，计划在香港市场发行创纪录数量的央行票据，以消化过剩流动性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/pboc-taps-record-bill-issuance-in-hong-kong-to-support-yuan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:02:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比看跌押注推动对冲成本升至 2022 年以来最高水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着越来越多的人押注印度当局正在放松对卢比的控制，对冲印度资产外汇风险的成本升至两年多来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-09/indian-rupee-hedging-costs-highest-since-2022-on-bearish-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 01:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国国债结束四天抛售，亚洲股市下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国债价格上涨，结束了连续四天的抛售潮。抛售潮是由对通胀持续上涨的担忧引发的，而当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的财政刺激计划可能会加剧通胀。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-08/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 08 Jan 2025 22:28:44 GMT</pubDate>
